    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine performs smoothly, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are functioning as intended. While the interior is well-kept and the exterior retains a great shine, you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful regular use. It offers a solid driving experience and is ready for the road without any immediate repairs needed.",
