    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive engineering, this vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing zero signs of wear, it represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail has been preserved with exacting care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example that drives with the same precision and grace as the day it left the factory. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48900.0,
